Class BasicTechAircraftData

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.techdata.BasicTechAircraftData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BasicTechAircraftData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class BasicTechAircraftData represents a basic technical information for Aircraft class such as maximum weight capacity, fuel spending in tons per kilometer, middle velocity in kilometers per hour and maximum people capacity of aircraft to transport.
